room_title: Escape room "Circus" by Escape Hotel in Los Angeles
room_description:
Welcome to room 1931. Are you ready for the show? Well, there is no show for you today. The circus is empty. Silence has never been so loud. The freaks have all left, but they will be back in an hour. Don’t forget; this place is full of tricks. Don’t believe what you hear or see…
Your goal is to travel back in time to see the famous murder of the Circus of 1931 and find Gambini's stolen mask. But as of now, the killer is still on the loose. Be smart and don't let the freaks play with your mind.
